Sprint #1 User Stories:
User Story 1: As a student, I want to create an account and set my dietary preferences, so UHS staff can view them and provide accurate meal recommendations. As admin (Alicia/UHS) staff, I want to view student dietary preferences, so that I can ensure meal ideas and recommendations align with their needs.
User Story 2: As an Admin (Alicia/UHS staff), I want to be able to add, edit, and delete recipes in the system, so that students always receive accurate, up-to-date meal options that support balanced nutrition.

